name: Spend an afternoon taking a look at the new features & enhancements in IBM SPSS
description:
Join us for an afternoon and take a look at the new and enhanced features of IBM SPSS Modeler 17 and Statistics 23.

Accelerate your knowledge and develop useful strategies on how to optimise IBM SPSS to simplify your data analysis.

The session is being hosted by premier IBM business partner, Cortell Australia. The event is a great opportunity to learn and network with top level SPSS users like yourself.

There is no charge for attending but space is limited, so if you’re interested in attending register quickly. A direct link to the full agenda and registration form can be found here http://tinyurl.com/qes5fyt
